review_blob: Lovely Yorkshire brewed bitter with a medium caramel flavour, refreshing creamy texture,its a drink to enjoy. My local brewery too.

Pauliner Brauahus are a german pub chain in Shanghai, Ive had this beer a few times while Ive been here, Its lacking in flavour, with a poor flavour lacking bite and taste, and usually served warm even though its supposed to be a lager/beer

Shocking!! 
Go to Castle Oktober Instead.
